                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                         stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                              d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"/>
                    </svg>
                </span>

                <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-700 capitalize white:text-white">Voir mes commandes</h1>

                <p class="text-gray-500 white:text-gray-300">
                    En cours de commande ou déjà commandez avant,
                    regardez l'avancé de votre commande et retrouvez vos factures ici !
                </p>

                <a href="{{ path('user_order') }}"
